00:31:51,797 --> 00:31:53,859
So one character might be on their way to an escape route,

775
00:31:53,859 --> 00:31:56,020
but they've got a lot of cool weapons and gadgets

776
00:31:56,020 --> 00:31:58,542
and things like that, so if they escape with it,

