00:33:41,713 --> 00:33:43,694
or large levels that are non-linear

816
00:33:43,694 --> 00:33:46,395
and the player can just beeline through and miss everything.

817
00:33:46,395 --> 00:33:47,955
Stuff like that, right?

818
00:33:50,702 --> 00:33:53,142
And so this is a single playthrough,

819
00:33:53,142 --> 00:33:54,042
a hypothetical single playthrough.

820
00:33:54,042 --> 00:33:56,783
There are a lot of diehards that will eat

821
00:33:56,783 --> 00:33:59,364
all the content in these games,

822
00:33:59,364 --> 00:34:00,444
but they're outliers.

823
00:34:00,444 --> 00:34:03,525
This is more like the average kind of playthrough

824
00:34:03,525 --> 00:34:04,905
in one of these spaces, right?

